<h1>Links and resources</h1>

<h2>Associations</h2>

<li><a href="http://www.sastat.org.za/">South African Statistical Association (SASA)</a></li>
<li><a href="http://www.biometricsociety.org/">International Biometric Society (IBS)</a></li>
<li><a href="http://www.fsf.org/">Free Software Foundation (FSF)</a></li>
<li><a href="http://foastat.org/">Foundation for Open Access Statistics (FOAS)</a></li>

<h2>Statistics</h2>

<li><a href="http://www.statsci.org/">Statistical Science Web.</a> A Statistics portal based in Australia, with teaching and research resources, job lists, and a large directory of contact details, mailing lists, etc.</li>
<li><a href="http://archive.ics.uci.edu/ml/">UCI Machine Learning repository.</a> Repository with many data sets, hosted by the University of California, Irvine.</li>

<h2>Computing</h2>

<li><a href="http://www.gnu.org/">GNU.</a> The GNU operating system, respecting your freedom.</li>
<li><a href="http://www.r-project.org/">R-project.</a> Free and open-source software for statistical computing.</li>
<li><a href="http://www.rstudio.com/">RStudio.</a> Integrated development environment (IDE) for R, for improved productivity.</li>
<li><a href="http://www.statmethods.net/">Quick-R.</a> Instructions on using R to perform various statistical procedures, written in an easily accessible style.</li>
<li><a href="http://en.wikibooks.org/wiki/LaTeX">LaTeX wikibook.</a> Online guide for using the LaTeX markup language to typeset documents.</li>
<li><a href="http://ubuntu.sun.ac.za/wiki/index.php/Main_Page">Maties Ubuntu.</a> Guide for using the Ubuntu GNU/Linux operating system on the Stellenbosch University campus.</li>
<li><a href="https://www0.sun.ac.za/hpc/index.php?title=Main_Page">Rhasatsha HPC.</a> Information about the high performance cluster (HPC) at Stellenbosch University.</li>

<h2>Books freely available online</h2>

<li><a href="http://web.stanford.edu/~hastie/local.ftp/Springer/ESLII_print10.pdf">The elements of statistical learning (2nd edition).</a> Trevor Hastie, Robert Tibshirani and Jerome Friedman (2009).</li> 

<li><a href="http://web.stanford.edu/~hastie/local.ftp/Springer/ISLR_print1.pdf">An introduction to statistical learning.</a> Gareth James, Daniela Witten, Trevor Hastie and Robert Tibshirani (2013).</li>

<li><a href="http://sourceforge.net/projects/linuxcommand/files/TLCL/13.07/TLCL-13.07.pdf/download">The Linux command line (2nd Internet edition).</a> William Shotts (2013).</li>

<li><a href="http://sens.tistory.com/attachment/cfile8.uf@2375DC3D515423F9110CA1.pdf">The art of R programming: A tour of statistical software design.</a> Norman Matloff (2011).</li>

